node.text:
Small in the frame. Antarctic penguins representing their small size in the vastness of Antarctica. A mix of Gentoo, Chinstrap and Adelie penguins.People tend to enjoy the close-up views of penguins, but personally, I revel in getting a penguin framed within its habitat, showing of the impressive scale of Antarctica. What do you prefer? 
All shot on canonr5  and RF100-500mm and RF50mm.
#canon #canonuk #canonnordic #penguin #Antarctica #bbcwildlifepotd #natgeoyourshot #wildlifephotography
